{
  "stem": "2620.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we all decided that it's best that you stay where you are, and I stay where I am.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'll come and visit you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was there already three times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, so-- so-- then-- so he remained over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, I just send them-- I send them packages, send him what he needs and help them out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what happened to me is I decided, as much as I liked the people I worked for, and they liked me, and I had a good job-- I became an inside salesman-- and filling the orders.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a wholesale men's haberdashery store over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I met up with some other friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we talked it over that we'll go to California-- go to Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we bought a car together, and we drove across country.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one of them is Eddie, Eddie [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we're still very good friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we find-- you know, worked on jobs, different jobs, and worked as a-- the first thing, we got a job as a-- door-to-door, selling dishes and silverware.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I-- my conscience was bothering me that they charged too much money and interest on the balance.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I just quit that job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I worked for a-- other wholesale stores, you know, a haberdashery, and clothing, and costume jewelry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I find a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I see an ad in the paper where Douglas Aircraft was hiring.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I made up an -- filled out an application, and I-- I got hired.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a stock clerk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I worked as a stock clerk and then got into different classifications-- expediter, and this and that, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
